summary: I am a passionate person about law with the aim of achieving a safe and fair environment in any professional industry. Native Spanish and fully fluent English speaker with an easy adaptation to multicultural teams. Throughout my professional career, I have built solid strengths focused mainly on ensuring that an organization complies with all laws, regulations and ethical standards applicable to its activity, specially in the Gaming Industry (iGaming and Landbased). My main functions are focused on developing and implementing compliance programs and procedures that ensure compliance with the organization's internal regulations and policies.
